right: COL title VAL "Custom Engraved 3 Liter Oak Barrels for Aging Whiskey, Rum, Tequila, Bourbon, Scotch and Wine (3 liter)" COL feature VAL "Authentic 3 Liter Charred White American Oak Aging Barrel. 3L holds close to about 3/4 gallon Includes: Stand, Bung, Spigot, Instructions, Paper Funnel Wooden barrel stand design may vary Choose engraving from our library of images, Upload your own image or just add text Top manufacturer of oak barrels in U.S. with highest customer satisfaction rating" COL description VAL "Do you like getting more drink for your buck? The only difference between bottom shelf and top shelf liquor is that it was aged longer. How would you like the 20 year scotch taste for the 8 year old price? Or, turn your cheap bottle of whiskey, tequila, rum, bourbon, scotch, brandy or cognac in to a delicious bottle of single barrel, hand crafted reserve? What took them years to do in a large 55 gallon oak barrel you can do at home in just a few weeks. You can! You can also take a $40 bottle of wine and turn it in to a $400 bottle of wine. You can do it all in a Red Head Oak Barrel in just 4  6 weeks. These mini American Oak barrels are hand-made by a multi-generational Cooper. They make great gifts since they can be custom engraved for personal pride or great for corporate branding. You can now age and flavor your liquor and wine to the taste you prefer. Our oak barrels are available by size. The size of the barrel is determined by the number of Liters it will hold such as a One Liter Barrel holds 1 Liter or your standard liquor bottle whereas a Twenty Liter Barrel holds roughly 5 Gallons. We also offer Cigar Infusing Barrels. These American white oak barrels are charred on the inside, which is a process that caramelizes the sugar in the wood. Your favorite alcohol is poured into the barrel, sealed with a bung and aged to add depth and character. The spirit (or wine) literally pulls flavor out of the wood, infusing the liquid with earthy and vanilla tones. Hotter temperatures expand the spirit, pushing it into the wood and cooler temperatures draw the liquid and flavor out. This process is repeated everyday, for months. The barrels are pressure sealed with steel hoops, can be engraved with the design of your choice, and comes with a spigot, bung and stand. Red Head Oak Barrels American Oak Aging Barrels are available with or without engravings. Perfect for aging any store bought spirit (or even moonshine) or custom cocktail"

left: COL title VAL "ThinkBamboo 180g Bamboo Charcoal Odor Absorbing Refrigerator Pouch - 3pc Black" COL feature VAL "3 Black Granulated Bamboo Charcoal Odor Absorbing Air Fresheners. Trap and destroy refrigerator odors, and help prevent flavor contamination. These perfume-free air-fresheners work by trapping odors, and are much more effective and fast acting than the traditional box of baking soda. Put one in each crisper drawer, and one on the top shelf to control odors and prolong the life you your fresh produce. Put them in your freezer to prevent ice cubes from picking up flavors. Re-usable, to recharge the odor absorbing and destroying power of the bamboo charcoal, simply lay the air freshener out in bright sunlight. These air fresheners each measure approximately 6" X 5" X 1 1/2" and contain 180 grams of Bamboo Charcoal." COL description VAL "These Bamboo Charcoal air fresheners are much more effective than baking soda at absorbing and controlling refrigerator odors. Each packet holds 180 grams of activated carbon derived from environmentally friendly bamboo. Activated Carbon is a natural air purifier, and has a surface area as high as 600 sq meters per gram, and is excellent at absorbing and trapping bacteria and odors which can cause flavor contamination between foods in your refrigerator.The bamboo charcoal not only absorbs odors, but extends the life of your fresh produce as well. It does this by acting as a natural humidity regulator and by absorbing the ethylene gas that fruits and vegetables naturally emit as they ripen. Bamboo Charcoal products are new to the market, but were so sure youll be pleased that we offer a money back guarantee.To use, just place one packet in each of your refrigerators crisper drawers, and one in the back of the top shelf. These can be re-used for up to 1 year, but for best results, we recommend that you replace them twice a year. Once they have been exhausted, you can cut them open and spread the charcoal on your garden or lawn as fertilizer. To keep them working at their best, just lay the bags out in bright sunlight for a couple hours twice every month to regenerate their odor absorbing power.Bamboo charcoal isn't just great for your refrigerator and freezer. Customers have told us that they use these in their closets, bathrooms, and laundry rooms as well as near litter boxes to help control pet odors. Now available in 3 colors to keep them separate if you're using them in multiple locations."

Used since ancient times as a decoration and a source of light, the diya is an oil lamp that burns vegetable oil or ghee Indian butter. COL title VAL "Soma Sustainable Carafe & Plant-Based Water Filter" COL feature VAL "Shatter-resistant glass carafe Holds 6 glasses (48oz) of fresh filtered water Lid door opens automatically for easy filling Glass, cone, and lid are dishwasher-safe Designed and assembled in California" COL description VAL "
Soma is on a mission to improve life for everyone who drinks water, with sustainable, plant-based filters that make water healthy and delicious, beautiful carafes and pitchers, and the convenient Filters by Mail service.
The Soma Pitcher is made of shatter-proof, BPA-free plastic. Designed to look stunning on your table and fit perfectly in your fridge, the pitcher holds 10-cups (80 oz) of crisp, refreshing filtered water.
Easy-to-fill and featuring Somas unique filter made of coconut shell carbon and plant-based casing that removes chlorine and improves taste. And for every Soma filter purchased, clean drinking water is donated to people in need through Somas nonprofit partner, charity: water. Raise your glass with the Soma water filter.
Our Mission
We believe clean drinking water is a basic human right. Thats why were a proud sponsor of charity: water and partner with them in their mission to bring safe drinking water to over 750 million people without access to it. Every time you buy a Soma filter, we donate to charity: water projects. These contributions go directly to sustainable, community-owned water projects in developing countries. We want our customers to feel good about their water, so we strive to find ways to not only create more sustainable business practices, but to find solutions to the global water crisis. As a certified B-corporation, impact is a critical part of Soma's DNA. We infuse it into everything we do, from our product design and supply chain to our company culture and partnerships. Soma's German-engineered glass carafe is shatter-resistant, and keeps water crisp and fresh. It holds 48 oz (6 cups) of fresh filtered water. The Soma filter features coconut shell carbon and a plant-based casing so you can feel good about your water. Each filter is effective for 40 gallons, or about two months. The Water Quality Association has tested and certified the Soma filter to NSF/ANSI Standard 42 requirements for the reduction of chlorine, taste and odor. Because polluting water while manufacturing products that enhance water wouldnt make any sense at all. One night during a dinner party, our founder, Mike del Ponte was hesitant to put his cheap plastic other brand water filter on his nicely set table. Mike decided to pour his filtered water into a glass wine decanter. Unfortunately (or fortunately) as he did, the lid of the water pitcher fell off, causing water to gush all over the kitchen floor. As he cleaned up the mess, he thought, Why cant someone create a water filter thats beautifully designed, easy to use, and made of sustainable materials? Soma was born. The rest is water under the bridge. Soma is the only water filter with 100% plant-based filtration. Distinguished by its clean, modern design, Soma also gives back by donating clean drinking water to those in need through charity: water. The most difficult part of designing Soma's first product, the Carafe, was finding glass that is both lightweight and durable. We discovered borosilicate glass by the famous German glass maker Schott. Though it took over a year, this discovery is what makes the Carafe a joy to use."

Condar fireplace screens DO NOT include a rod." COL description VAL "Enhance the style of your fireplace with a Condar mesh screen.

Condars attractive fireplace mesh screens make your fireplace the center piece of any room. Functional, visually appealing, and made to last.

All Condar screen packages include:

Two panels, totaling 48 inches wide.
19 gauge steel mesh.
1/4 inch openings in the mesh.
1/2 inch hanger rings.
Matte black finish.
A pair of matching Cool Grip screen pulls.

All screen packages include two panels, totaling 48 inches wide. This is sufficient for an attractive natural drape effect on most fireplaces and inserts. Standard screen sizes range from 16 inches through 36 inches tall.


How to choose the right size screen for your fireplace:

Just measure the height and width of your current screen (not including hanger rings) and order the same height screen. Condar's hanger rings will add half inch (1 cm) to total height.

Buying a screen and already have a rod installed?

If you already have a rod installed, measure the height of your fireplace opening to the top of the rod. Subtract inch (1 cm) for the hanger rings below the rod, and approximately inch (1 cm) for clearance at the bottom (1 inch: 3 cm total).

Condar fireplace screens do not include a rod.

If you dont have a fireplace screen rod installed, choose the Rod and Valance Kit (ASIN: B0039ZD9O2). IMPORTANT: When ordering both Rod and Valance Kit and screen choose a screen size 2 inches (5 cm) shorter than the height of your fireplace opening (this accounts for hanger rings and clearance at the bottom).

Now available in Stainless Steel (Amazon ASIN: B01ND4CLXI)."

The heat from the aluminum wick collar will warm and "blossom" or "throw" the fragrance. Please note, the aroma deck does not get as hot as a tea light burner and, therefore, the scent may not be as heavy. The candle flame is also protected by the integrated wind shield. The famous art masterpieces are selected for their visual beauty and then applied to a special shaped vase design with a cut edge to enhance a design element from the painting.

Vincent van Gogh (1853-1890)
Post-impressionist painter Van Gogh was a huge influence on developments in 20th-century art. He however did not live to see his artistry recognized and during his life only a single work was sold. At the age of 37, the lonely artist, committed suicide driven to despair by a destructive psychological affliction. After a decade of prolific drawing and painting, he left behind a substantial oeuvre which provided an important stimulus to artistic movements such as Fauvism and Expressionism. He is know for thick application of paint, a technique called impasto, which adds a textural surface to the canvas and forever leaves behind a visual signature of Van Gogh's artistry.

Irises by Van Gogh (1889)
Van Gogh painted the irises shortly after having himself voluntarily committed to the psychiatric institution Saint Paul-de-Mausole. He referred to the painting as a lightning rod for my illness because he hoped that by painting constantly he could avoid descending into madness. The painting Irises is clearly influence"

This dehumidifiers absorb the moisture from the surrounding area by dessicant (silica gel).
There is a built-in heater that will warm the crystals allowing them to expand and release the moisture as water vapor into the outside air.
Since this product does not use any batteries or electrical wires, there is no worry of electrical haphazard.
Our dehumidifers is renewable, will not require any expensive refills.

How to Recharge / Renew?

After the launch of the plug, the indicator light will light, It takes 3-5 hours to recharge.
When the silica gels in the indicator window become deep blue.
Unplug charger and let the dehumidifier stand about 20-30 minutes to cool down.
Then the dehumidifier is renewed and ready to be used again.
Put it in a suitable location.
When silica gels are full, they will turn into pink. Then the dehumidifier need to be recharged again.
While charging, please place the dehumidifier in a well-ventilated area, preferably next to a window, avoid the moisture to reenter the air from and pulled it in the first place.

Closets : protect the clothes from dampness
Plastic storage containers : protect cameras lens of fog
Cabinets : stamps, photographs from corrosion
Under sink : keep in moisture free
Safes : money or important from dampness

COL title VAL "Japanese Matcha Bowl Rabbit KUTANI YAKI(ware)" COL feature VAL "Made in Japan, in Ishikawa Famous Japanese traditional Pottery KUTANI since 1655 Size:(H) 2.5inches x (D) 4.3inches" COL description VAL "Japan KUTANI
A stone monument bearing the inscription "Ko-Kutani kiln ruins" stands quietly in a clearing.
It marks the spot where the Daishouji Clan(a branch of the Kaga Clan)
established a kiln in about 1655,to make use of the local porcelain stone.
Tha porcelain ware that was created there was later called "Ko-kutani"
and became the foundation for Japanese colored porcelain ware.
Rich overglaze colors applied with fluid brushwork -green,yellow,red,purple and blue-
give Kutani porcelain its characteristic beauty.
However,only half a century later the kiln was abandoned for reasons that nobody knows.

About 100 years later,Kutani porcelain was revived under the patronage of the Kaga clan.
The Kasugayama and Wakasugi kilns were established, and kilns such as the Yoshidaya kiln
rode on the momentum of "revived Kutani",all producing overglaze porcelain ware.
Various styles competed and combined to develop into the overglaze techniques
that have been handed down to this day.

In modern times,the gorgeous Kinrande style(very high-quality design of gold)
has become well known in the West as "Japan Kutani"

COL title VAL "Pickl-It Deluxe Fermentation Lid Kit Convert 'Fido' Jars For Anaerobic Pickling" COL feature VAL "Our airtight-lid and airlock system are the same practical tools used by our ancient ancestors Many Pickl-It customers have switched from canning to Pickl-It fermentation, preserving their precious food Glass-Lid - Made in Italy Silicone grommet USA-made FDA food-grade Barrel Air Lock One-way valve releases excess CO2 and oxygen, creating natural, spontaneous anaerobic conditions" COL description VAL "Pickl-It Practicality
Our airtight-lid and airlock system are the same practical tools used by our ancient ancestors. They used animal skins, unglazed covered crocks, sealed gourds, covered wooden barrels, and deep-earth fermentation pits. We use glass, salt and water to achieve the same great results. No animals were harmed in Pickl-it Development.

Pickl-It Protects
Weve put anaerobic oxygen-free back into fermentation. When oxygen is eliminated, the bad guys, like mold and harmful yeasts, cannot thrive. And the good guys vitamins, antioxidants, important dietary enzymes, and probiotics thrive in an anaerobic environment.

Pickl-It Preserves
Many Pickl-It customers have switched from canning to Pickl-It fermentation, preserving their precious food. Foods fermented and stored in the Pickl-It system remain viable, flavorful and nutritious from harvest-to-harvest, or longer. You can expect an 18-month life for sauerkraut, pickled cucumbers, kimchi, garlic, lemons and hot pepper mashes.

Each Pickl-It lid-kit includes;
- Hand-made in USA, Pickl-It food-grade glass fermenting lid
- Food grade silicone grommet
- 3-piece primary fermentation airlock
- Silicone PlugR

Deluxe lid-kit also includes;
- 3oz DunkR glass fire-polished fermentation weight
- 1/4 pound ice white brine-grind fermentation sea salt
- All glass Italian food-grade container lid
"

left: COL title VAL "Viva Self Cleaning Stainless Steel Bottom Loading Water Cooler" COL feature VAL "Self cleans the water cooler automatically several times a day, preventing buildup of bacterial biofilm True appliance grade stainless steel water dispenser front, not silver painted, or stainless steel 'look' Ice chill cooling keeps the water cooler at a steady 40F, always refreshingly frigid. Most water coolers temperatures typically reach up to 50F Steaming, instant hot water is kept in a narrow range between 176 to 198F, ideal for making robustly flavored tea. This bottom loading water dispenser hides the 3 or 5 gallon water bottles in the bottom." COL description VAL "From the manufacturer: This gorgeous full stainless steel front water cooler hides the bottle out of sight. It is true stainless steel, the type used in high end kitchen appliances, making this water dispenser a perfect fit for the modern kitchen and office. The self cleaning is done automatically with unstable oxygen, which rips apart the bacteria that makes biofilm in regular water coolers. The self cleaning runs several times a day, and keeps the water tasting fresh. The water itself is kept at an optimum temperature. One frustrating thing about water coolers is that they do not cool water as cold as a refrigerator (40F), typically cooling up to 50F. Our ice cooling technology keeps the water at a chilly 40F, perfect for those hot summer days. The instant hot water system keeps its temperature in a narrow range, always steaming hot, so that tea is made properly. According to ancient Chinese cosmology (dated from around 6,000 BC), the universe was divided into four quadrants marking the beginning and end of the winter and summer solstices and the fall and spring equinoxes (see yin yang). Each quadrant was visible in its entirety only in the season with which it is associated. These heavenly quadrants were called the Four Celestial Palaces, and each "palace" was represented by a guardian animal, the Dragon - Spring, Phoenix - Summer, Tiger - Fall and Turtle - Winter. Dragon: Also known as dragon is the highest spiritual power, the divine power of change and transformation, the rhythms of nature, supernatural wisdom and strength. It is often portrayed carrying the pearl of wisdom, enlightenment and spiritual essence of the universe. The Azure Dragon represents Spring and the direction East. Phoenix: Its various elements represent the cosmos: The head of a cock is the sun, the back of a swallow is the moon, its wings are the wind, its tail are the trees and flowers and its feet are the earth. The phoenix is a universal symbol of resurrection and immortality, of death and rebirth by fire. The phoenix represents Summer and the direction South. Tiger:The white tiger represents authority, courage, prowess and fierceness needed for protection. It also represents Autumn and the direction West. When the celestial tiger is paired with the celestial dragon (green) it provides supreme protection and good fortune. Turtle: This turtle (synonomous wth tortoise) is also referred to as the Black Warrior because of its strength, endurance and longevity. It represents Winter and the direction North."

COL title VAL "hölm Kitchen Collection Professional Ergonomic Smooth Edge, Side Cut Manual Can Opener. Kitchen Cans, Lid Lifter with Easy Turn Design and Soft Grips Handle - Red" COL feature VAL "ERGONOMIC - No more struggling to open cans. Fits easily in your hand.The handle is long enough and thick enough to give a good grip so your hands wont cramp while opening the can. The handle is also textured with a tacky rubber for traction so you can get a good grip. The handle is also longer than a standard can opener handle for better leverage and easier turning. SMOOTH CUTS - Creates a smooth edge on any can it opens so you won't have to worry about slicing your hand by accident. The can opener LIFTS the lid right off without slicing through metal. It undoes the seem that holds the can to the can lid. SIDE CUT - By far the safest way to open a can is with a side cutting can opener such as this one. Although called a "side cut" the opened actually doesn't slice through metal. It releases the lid from the can so it just pops right off like a jar lid. OPENS LIKE A JAR - No need to struggle to turn the handle as the opener's blade removes the lid just like a jar lid." COL description VAL "The first can opener was patented in 1858. At the time, most cans were a opened with a hammer and chisel. Lucky for you, technology has improved.

The modern day can opener works by cutting into the top of the can, leaving jagged edges. At Holm, we felt that there was a better and safer way. We designed our can opener to separate the lid from the body of the can, leaving dull safe edges. Since the can opener doesn't have to slice through metal, it's easier and safer to operate than the old-fashioned can openers.

We tested the holm lid lifter with right handed and left handed cooks and opened hundreds of cans: squat cans of tuna fish, small cans of tomato paste, medium cans of chickpeas, and large cans of whole tomatoes. We also made sure our can opener was easy to attach to the cans. Next, we designed the can opener for smoothness and ease of operation. We wanted it to be easy to drive the opener around cans. The handle is ergonomic - not too thin, or too thick.

Finally, we made sure our design made for a safe lid detachment and disposal. Since the lid is separated from the can, it's an easy process to simply remove it when it is completely severedsafe, clean, and simple. No sharp edges to deal with.

In the end we asked ourselves one all important question: Can you be in love with a can opener? We think so. Our can opener is easy to attach and operate, tidily and safely disposes of lids. Compared with your grandma's old style can opener, this opener will seem like magic."

BISSELL Portable Deep Cleaner FAQ

Why should I invest in a spot cleaner?
Unlike sprays and foams, the SpotClean permanently removes deep-down dirt, spots and stains. With sprays, stains find a way of coming back, but the SpotClean makes sure that theyre gonefor good.

Why is it better than spray or foam?
Unlike a spray that goes on and cleans the surface of stains, spot cleaners combine hot water, targeted cleaning formula, and powerful suction to get deep down in the exact spot you need it.

Are upright or portable deep cleaners better?
When it comes to upright deep cleaners versus portable deep cleaners, its not about which is better, its about which is best suited for the job at hand. Uprights are best suited for large areas and whole rooms, while portable spot cleaners specialize in stairs, upholstery, auto interiors, and more.

left: COL title VAL "NewAir WAT30B Water Dispenser, Black" COL feature VAL "Features a bottle spike for easy, no spill 3 or 5 gallon bottle replacements Choose between refreshing cold, piping hot or room temperature water outputs for cool drinks or heated beverages Don't spend excess money on electricity with this Energy Star approved water cooler BPA Free and NSF Certified water dispenser provides only pure, clean water Reliable, child safety lock prevents children from using the hot water so you can use it worry free. The water is heated and cooled in a stainless steel tank using an energy-efficient compressor. It dispenses cold water at 39 Degree and hot water at 185 Degree. There's also a third option that allows you dispense water at room temperature. Ensures Healthy Drinking Water with 100% BPA-Free Material The NewAir WAT30B is made with 100% BPA-free materials. BPA is a synthetic organic compound used to strengthen certain types of plastic. When it's used in water coolers, it can seep into the water and damage your health. NewAir is committed to the highest levels of quality and safety, that's why our water coolers are made without BPA, so they deliver not only pure, clean, delicious water, but peace of mind for our customers. Includes a Built-In Bottle Spike That Prevents Spills & Makes it Easy to Load In order to prevent the water from leaking while you're inserting the bottle, the NewAir WAT30B has been built with a bottle spike inside the top of the unit. When you lower the bottle into the dispenser, the spike punctures a hole in the cap. The water slowly drains out into the reservoir without any spills whatsoever. Air bubbles up into the bottles as the reservoir is filled. When the bubbles stop, the unit is ready to start dispensing water. Includes a Child Safety Lock on the Hot Water Faucet Because the WAT30B dispenses water at such a high temperature, a safety lock has been installed on the hot water faucet in order to ensure the safety of your little ones and prevent them from accidentally scalding themselves. It guarantees your experience is always safe and reliable, two features always available from NewAir products."

Worshipped as the God of Fire, he also presided over metallurgy, crafting, weaving, and served as protector of the weak. Lughnasadh, the Sabbat celebrated in August, is named for him. A primary deity of the Druids, Lugh sometimes took human form and worshipped alongside them. He is a wonderful God to call upon when one doesn't know how to proceed, because he can do or assist with anything. Lugh is often associated with the Greek God Apollo, and more statues and holy sites were erected to this handsome God than to any other Celtic deity. The inscription on the base was written and conceived by author Raven Grimassi."

Among the filtration media employed is a natural carbon filter that captures microscopic particles. Charcoal carbon is a natural material that operates on the adsorption principle. It provides a vast amount of surface area for adsorption, and thus makes an extremely effective filter medium. PRODUCE ALKALINE WATER: PiMag Water Technology adds natural minerals and adjusts pH value to 8.5-9.5 range (alkaline) to help counterbalance a largely acidic modern environment. Corrosion-protected magnets produce a magnetic field surrounding the direction of water flow to reduce sediment agglomeration. GOOD FOR HEALTH: Higher pH (or alkaline) water is now seen by many as an essential component of their daily intake of liquids, contributing towards better body balance by counteracting the increased acidity of our modern diets. It is believed that alkaline water with a low oxidisation reduction potential (ORP) helps restore this balance while also helping to defend your body against illness. CONVENIENT AND PORTABLE: The Waterfall needs no electricity or plumbed-in water source, so is easily set up straight out of the box. Tap water is simply poured into the top of the gravity fed system and passes through the filter, over mineral stones, and finally through a magnetic field, before being dispensed as pure energised Nikken water. Designed to fit neatly on kitchen worktops and underneath standard kitchen cupboards. GOLD SEAL FILTRATION: The Nikken Waterfall has received the coveted Gold Seal of Approval from the Water Quality Association of America. This accreditation is only given to water treatment systems that meet rigorous standards for performance, capacity, and integrity, in removing a variety of drinking water contaminants. Please be aware that unit may have either LED or No LED Feature for the Waterfall System. All the new System has no longer have the lights/LED feature." FEATURES & BENEFITS
  • A regulated acid/alkaline (pH) balance is essential for maintaining health, but a typical modern diet and lifestyle can lead to excess acidity.
  • Ionized water decreases oxidation-reduction potential. A high ORP contributes to unwanted oxidative decomposition. Ionized PiMag water from the Waterfall can help offset the oxidizing effect of many elements of the modern diet and environment. This can actually help slow down cellular destruction.
  • Commercially bottled water is not only expensive, the quality or level of contamination can vary depending on where or when it was bottled. The PiMag Waterfall provides consistent quality.
  • The PiMag Waterfall is environmentally responsible. It reduces the number of discarded, disposable water bottles that become trash in landfills. This also decreases consumption of fossil fuels used in manufacturing those bottles.

COL title VAL "Albert Einstein Art Print Abstract Modern Artwork Signed on Metal | Wall Art QT" COL feature VAL "Signed Collectible Made in USA Albert Einstein wall decor art print by Mark Lewis Art Modern art collectible 8" x 10" on metal signed by the artist Original H/E edition abstract artwork Ancestor of Cy Young the baseball legend 10th Grandson to a founder of Portsmouth Rhode Island" COL description VAL "ALBERT EINSTEIN ART PRINT

Now own a personally signed abstract modern metal art print of celebrity star ALBERT EINSTEIN by artist Mark Lewis Art . This is a special H/E edition metal art print created from an original painting titled "QUESTIONING TOMORROW" Lewis' eye catching wall decor metal art prints are ideal for any room in your home. Lewis hails from a long line of decorative pop art artists and uses aluminum as the foundation to ensure a pure and brilliant, 3-D looking image of nothing other than his unique enchanting collections of famous modern and abstract pop art portraits he has created throughout his artistic career. Each simply incredible 8x 10 HDR image comes with a 3-d wall mount, a certificate of authenticity and a plate on the reverse with the artistic hand signature of Mark Lewis. Your personal order will arrive in a well-padded package for safe shipping.

ABOUT MARK LEWIS ART

Why should you invest in Mark Lewis art today? Because in addition to its own artistic significance, this piece has fascinating relevance to the cultural and political history of the United States. The artist Mark Lewis is one of only a few surviving relatives (and the last in his lineage) of baseball legend Cy Young, the winning-est pitcher in MLB history. Mark is also the 10th Great Grandson of Richard Carder, who was one of the 23 signers of the first document in American history that severed both political and religious ties with England (the Portsmouth Compact in 1636) and formed a colony that would eventually become Portsmouth, Rhode Island. Due to these unique ancestral ties to such significant members of American history, combined with Mark's own artistic talent for painting and recreating famous photographs of Pop Culture icons, we believe that this piece is a sound investment for collectors of modern and contemporary American art.

left: COL title VAL "Large 1-screw Replacement Handle for Revere Ware Pans" COL feature VAL "Large 1-screw replacement handle for Revere Ware pans Includes necessary hardware" COL description VAL "These are large sized replacement handles for newer era Revere Ware pans. These parts are newly manufactured and are made to look and work just like original Revere Ware handles. Material: Bakelite, stainless steel, aluminum Includes: One handle + hardware set IF YOU GET A HANDLE MISSING THE HARDWARE, PLEASE CONTACT US AND WE WILL SEND YOU THE HARDWARE SEPARATELY. Measurements: 5.6 in (142 mm) long overall, 4.8 in (122 mm) long Bakelite Fits: Newer style 2 quart and 3 quart sauce pans and similar handled steamer baskets, 8 inch skillets; both copper bottom and tri-ply aluminum core varieties, and possibly others. These fit Revere Ware cookware with handles that have one screw through the metal part of the handle. Note that all sizes of this type of handle (small, medium, large, and x-large) have the same size metal spline at the end, so they will fit any pot that accepts this type of handle, although a large handle on a very small pot might be visually unappealing. Please use the measurements above to insure you choose a proper size. Replaces: Revere called this handle style "Style No. 3" and "one-piece". The original Revere part number for this handle (large size) was 36031. It also had an older part number of the 4xx type that we have not been able to determine. Hardware Notes The screw in the hardware set is Phillips head, not slotted like some of the original Revere Ware screw sets were (most of these handles were riveted, not screwed on). Because the original slot head screws strip very easily, we consider this an improvement. Bakelite Notes It is not a good idea to put these handles in the oven and we do not offer them as oven-safe. Washing in a dishwasher will dull the finish on the Bakelite. Installation Notes To remove the rivet on the old handle, drill it out with a 5/32 drill bit."

Made in the U.S.A. U.S. Patent #s 7,468,203 B2 / 8,007,896 / Other U.S. & Foreign Patents Pending Bird-window collisions (BWCs) are the largest human-caused factor in bird mortality. It is estimated that in the United States alone that nearly a billion birds are killed annually from BWCs. A leading theory attributes BWCs to reflection of habitat in windows (e.g. a bird will mistake the reflection of a tree for the actual tree). Artscape has developed a new product to reduce the impact of window-collisions on bird populations. The solution is a product that emits light where bird vision is sensitive but human vision is not. This allows birds to differentiate reflections in windows from actual habitat while remaining aesthetically pleasing to people."

The original masterpiece was created in 1889. Today it has been carefully recreated detail-by-detail, color-by-color to near perfection. Van Gogh created copies of his own work while in St. Remy asylum. The sunflower paintings reminded him of the happy days spent in a yellow house with another artist. By reproducing his own work he balked at the notion of supremacy for the "one-off" and "never-to-be-repeated" original. In fact he repainted his images so that he might retain a copy of what he gave away to friends. Vincent Van Gogh's restless spirit and depressive mental state fired his artistic work with great joy and, sadly, equally great despair. Known as a prolific Post-Impressionist, he produced many paintings that were heavily biographical. This work of art has the same emotions and beauty as the original. PRODUCE ALKALINE WATER: PiMag Water Technology adds natural minerals and adjusts pH value to 8.5-9.5 range (alkaline) to help counterbalance a largely acidic modern environment. Corrosion-protected magnets produce a magnetic field surrounding the direction of water flow to reduce sediment agglomeration. It is believed that alkaline water with a low oxidisation reduction potential (ORP) helps restore this balance while also helping to defend your body against illness. CONVENIENT AND PORTABLE: The Waterfall needs no electricity or plumbed-in water source, so is easily set up straight out of the box. Tap water is simply poured into the top of the gravity fed system and passes through the filter, over mineral stones, and finally through a magnetic field, before being dispensed as pure energised Nikken water. GOLD SEAL FILTRATION: The Nikken Waterfall has received the coveted Gold Seal of Approval from the Water Quality Association of America. This accreditation is only given to water treatment systems that meet rigorous standards for performance, capacity, and integrity, in removing a variety of drinking water contaminants. Please be aware that unit may have either LED or No LED Feature for the Waterfall System. All the new System has no longer have the lights/LED feature." Because the PiMag Waterfall works without electricity or plumbing, it can be used in any location. FEATURES & BENEFITS
  • A regulated acid/alkaline (pH) balance is essential for maintaining health, but a typical modern diet and lifestyle can lead to excess acidity.

ABOUT MARK LEWIS ART

Why should you buy Mark Lewis art today? Because in addition to its own artistic significance, this piece has fascinating relevance to the cultural and political history of the United States. The artist Mark Lewis is one of only a few surviving relatives (and the last in his lineage) of baseball legend Cy Young, the winning-est pitcher in MLB history. Mark is also the 10th Great Grandson of Richard Carder, who was one of the 23 signers of the first document in American history that severed both political and religious ties with England (the Portsmouth Compact in 1636) and formed a colony that would eventually become Portsmouth, Rhode Island. Due to these unique ancestral ties to such significant members of American history, combined with Mark's own artistic talent for painting and recreating famous photographs of Pop Culture icons, we believe that this piece is a sound investment for collectors of modern and contemporary American art.

"
